Group Biography:
Milk & Honey is a German pop music duo consisting of singers Anne Ross and Manel Filali. German music producer Uwe Fahrenkrog-Petersen formed the duo under the Warner Music Group label in 2006.
Their first single, "Habibi (je t&#039;aime)", reached 16th place on the German singles charts and remained on the charts for 12 weeks. A music video for "Habibi (Je T&#039;aime)" was released on August 17, 2007.
